dataList.title: A Distant World
dataList.content: ... She is forever lost. Her consciousness is broken, scattered to a thousand places.
Shut up! You'll have to do much worse to make me give up!
Heathcliff the Erlking falls to his knees.
We were less than ten paces from the rooftop; we had to stop him from going up the stairs no matter what.
He is bound. I cannot hold him with these chains for much longer; neutralize the target as soon as possible.
